<main class="page">

<a href="/" class="back">
← Back to PanorOmics
</a>

<section class="hero">

<h1>
PanorOmics <span>Scientific Integrity</span>
</h1>

<p class="lead">
Scientific integrity is the foundation of PanorOmics. Our commitment to evidence-based
education, scientific accuracy, interdisciplinary excellence, responsible innovation,
and lifelong learning guides every aspect of our educational initiatives, research,
scientific communication, and future development.
</p>

<div class="badge">
🧬 Scientific Integrity Principles
</div>

</section>

<section class="section">

<h2>Our Commitment</h2>

<p>
Developed in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, with roots that trace back to Chicago,
PanorOmics was founded to advance Omics Sciences through education, research,
and innovation. We believe trust in science is earned through transparency,
accuracy, intellectual honesty, and a commitment to continuous learning.
These principles guide our work as we contribute to the evolving landscape
of systems biology, biotechnology, artificial intelligence, and human health.
</p>

</section>

<section class="section">

<h2>Core Principles</h2>

<div class="principles">

<div class="card">
<h3>Evidence-Based Education</h3>
<p>
Educational content is grounded in current scientific knowledge,
peer-reviewed literature, and established biological principles.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Scientific Accuracy & Transparency</h3>
<p>
We are committed to factual, transparent, and responsible scientific
communication that promotes trust, reproducibility, and informed decision-making.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Interdisciplinary Excellence</h3>
<p>
PanorOmics integrates biological, computational, data, and translational sciences
to foster a systems-level understanding of life.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Responsible Innovation</h3>
<p>
We support the ethical application of biotechnology, artificial intelligence,
and Omics Sciences in ways that advance discovery and improve human health.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Lifelong Learning</h3>
<p>
We support learners, educators, researchers, clinicians, and professionals
through accessible, rigorous, and globally connected scientific education.
</p>
</div>

</div>

<div class="quote">

<p>
"Scientific integrity is not a feature of PanorOmics. It is the foundation upon which PanorOmics is built."
</p>

</div>

<p class="footer-note">
Advancing Omics Sciences through education, research, and innovation.
</p>

</section>

</main>

</body>
